/../../../author/editor.html">editor</a></span></div></div></article></div><div class="col-xs-12 col-md-3"><article class="typography vertical"><div class="article-image medium"><a title="Twelve Tricky Questions for Tinubu" href="twelve-tricky-questions-for-tinubu"><div style="width:100%;height:0;padding-top:100%;position:relative"><img alt="Image" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" class="attachment-thumbnail" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent" sizes="100vw" srcSet="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.ariseplay.com%2Famg%2Fwww.thisdaylive.com%2Fuploads%2F26c019fa-editorial-special-pages06-745x450.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.ariseplay.com%2Famg%2Fwww.thisdaylive.com%2Fuploads%2F26c019fa-editorial-special-pages06-745x450.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.ariseplay.com%2Famg%2Fwww.thisdaylive.com%2Fuploads%2F26c019fa-editorial-special-pages06-745x450.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.ariseplay.com%2Famg%2Fwww.thisdaylive.com%2Fuploads%2F26c019fa-editorial-special-pages06-745x450.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.ariseplay.com%2Famg%2Fwww.thisdaylive.com%2Fuploads%2F26c019fa-editorial-special-pages06-745x450.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.ariseplay.com%2Famg%2Fwww.thisdaylive.com%2Fuploads%2F26c019fa-editorial-special-pages06-745x450.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.ariseplay.com%2Famg%2Fwww.thisdaylive.com%2Fuploads%2F26c019fa-editorial-special-pages06-745x450.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.ariseplay.com%2Famg%2Fwww.thisdaylive.com%2Fuploads%2F26c019fa-editorial-special-pages06-745x450.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="../../../../_next/image1fe1?url=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.ariseplay.com%2Famg%2Fwww.thisdaylive.com%2Fuploads%2F2